  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a clay pot or Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "Add cumin, coriander, paprika, and cinnamon. Cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add tempeh and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add chickpea broth and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer, covered, for 20 minutes.",
    "Add coconut cream and stir to combine.",
    "Top with pistachios and cilantro.",
    "Transfer to the oven and bake at 425°F (220°C) for 15-20 minutes or until the sauce is bubbly and the tempeh is caramelized.",
    "Garnish with additional cilantro and serve hot."
